{"tid":768912,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"薛之謙啲歌詞真係好中。","createTime":"2018-08-05T19:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T23:08:41.000Z","uid":197743,"like":24,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"918297af5256b4c89ff746cb5833c9a403cd45ab","tid":768912,"uid":197743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:29:38.000Z","msg":"首首歌都好痛<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">你還要我怎樣：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你還要我怎樣 要怎樣<br />\n你突然來的短信就夠我悲傷<br />\n我沒能力遺忘 你不用提醒我<br />\n哪怕結局就這樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">等我回家：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我不想辜負一次又一次的信任<br />\n或把我比作不能自控的小人<br />\n這世界太嘈雜 周邊都是假話<br />\n你能不能再找個理由 等我回家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 紳士：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你退半步的動作認真的嗎<br />\n小小的動作傷害還那麼大<br />\n我只能扮演個紳士<br />\n才能和你說說話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">下雨了：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雨還在下你聽得見嗎<br />\n是我的思念滴滴答答<br />\n滴入你的心就會想起我<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">曖昧：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能是現在感情 太珍貴<br />\n讓付出真心的人 好疲憊<br />\n誰不曾用過卑微的詞彙 想留住誰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我害怕：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近我表現的還可以<br />\n最近你已走到了哪裡<br />\n別在意隨便問問而已<br />\n都怪我才學會了愛情<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">啞巴：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可以當我啞巴一樣<br />\n你不會看見我的抵抗<br />\n請別怕我受傷<br />\n我自己會圓場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">演員：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可你曾經那麼愛我 幹嘛演出細節<br />\n我該變成什麼樣子 才能延緩厭倦<br />\n原來當愛放下防備後的這些那些<br />\n才是考驗<br />\n<br />\n一字一句都好傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好痛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4367eb9595f206217e7135c97353aab2cec532","tid":768912,"uid":170611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:33:35.000Z","msg":"啞巴喺人地寫比佢？"},{"pid":"100e21c76c080ce8e1285d155c4b1678e07e1937","tid":768912,"uid":197743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b4367eb9595f206217e7135c97353aab2cec532","tid":768912,"uid":170611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:33:35.000Z","msg":"啞巴喺人地寫比佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:37:13.000Z","msg":"好似係改過詞曲 如果錯咗係到講聲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d668163a2c6ad386c8d2bf16ed02f092ef32a94","tid":768912,"uid":170611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"100e21c76c080ce8e1285d155c4b1678e07e1937","tid":768912,"uid":197743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b4367eb9595f206217e7135c97353aab2cec532","tid":768912,"uid":170611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:33:35.000Z","msg":"啞巴喺人地寫比佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:37:13.000Z","msg":"好似係改過詞曲 如果錯咗係到講聲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:48:45.000Z","msg":"唔緊要 都喺佢唱 <br />\n就好似喺汪蘇瀧作"},{"pid":"a8891e107247138f8c6f7674dcc3fc23896acfd7","tid":768912,"uid":27251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:56:51.000Z","msg":"認真的雪呢"},{"pid":"c513ea007b1a72a0f0051f02185e7a0740bd68be","tid":768912,"uid":72990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:57:38.000Z","msg":"Facebook呀呢到？屌你老母"},{"pid":"baa464a75f5da59256814b2b46c6a280cc714ddb","tid":768912,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T19:58:12.000Z","msg":"邊能個黎架-.-"},{"pid":"2697d71be3bc2397855e2a43004e704be10106e1","tid":768912,"uid":197743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8891e107247138f8c6f7674dcc3fc23